    dc:description "Fig. 1. Dardanus aspersus (Berthold, 1845), holotype of Pagurus watasei Terao, 1913, female (cl 16.7mm), UMUTZ-Crs-33. A, entire animal, dorsal view; B, shield and cephalic appendages, dorsal view; C, left cheliped, outer view; D, right cheliped, outer view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4584843/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4584847>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Dardanus aspersus (Berthold, 1845), holotype of Pagurus watasei Terao, 1913, female (cl 16.7mm), UMUTZ-Crs-33. A, left second and third pereopods, lateral view; B, right second and third pereopods, lateral view; C, left fourth pereopod, lateral view; D, sixth pleonal tergite and telson, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4584847/files/figure.png" ;
